channel.description:
Ok First off the server is open. But im in need of a development team to keep the server up and running since i cannot do this all on my own.
im wanting to start the server off with new shops new bosses, like nex.
We need better graphics and many players im also wanting a webclient.
I need the best staff team we can get. as of coders and developers.
